abstract: Washington Huskies head coach Chris Petersen signs two-year extension of his existing contract through 2020 season; other college football news noted.
lead_paragraph: DeAndre Washington ran for 173 yards and two touchdowns as Texas Tech (7-5, 4-5 Big 12) beat the Texas Longhorns, 48-45.

headline.main: Texas Tech Picks Up Rare Win in Rivalry With Texas
headline.print_headline: Texas Tech Picks Up Rare Road Win Against Texas

snippet: DeAndre Washington ran for 173 yards and two touchdowns as Texas Tech (7-5, 4-5 Big 12) beat the Texas Longhorns, 48-45.
